<hr>
<strong>Answers:  (1)</strong> 2, 4, 2, 4=20
<strong> (2)</strong> 5090 (3 significant figures - round to the tens place=
 - set by 550)
<strong>(3)</strong> 0.03 (1 significant figure - round to hundredths place=
)=20
<strong>(4)</strong> 7.4 x 10<sup>7</sup> (2 significant figures - set by 1=
.3 x 10<sup>3</sup>)
<strong>(5)</strong> 6.3 x 10<sup>5</sup> (2 significant figures - set by 0=
.010)
